            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-10-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-05-04T18:00:00-05:00" n="316" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d316">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Security Council discussed the question of the governorship of the Free
                    Territory of Trieste at its 233rd and 265th meetings which were held
                    respectively on January 23 and March 9, 1948. For the record of these
                    discussions see United Nations, <hi rend="italic">Official Records of the
                        Security Council, Third Year</hi>, Numbers 1–15, 233rd meeting, pages
                    204–207, and <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, Numbers 36–51, 265th meeting, pages
                    65–66.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
